text: Ugolino da Gualdo Cattaneo was an Roman Catholic professed religious and monk of the Order of Saint Augustine. He was born in 1200 and died on January 1, 1260.Saints and Blesseds == References == Category:1200 births Category:1260 deaths Category:Beatified people Category:People from Umbria
title: Ugolino da Gualdo Cattaneo
